>> # Are you aged between 16 and 25 years old living with Type 1 diabetes?
>> We know that young people with Type 1 diabetes themselves are the experts
in their own lives and have a lot of useful knowledge worth sharing about how
to deal with the many challenges of their condition.
>Our award winning Young Leaders project enables and encourages young people
> living with Type 1 diabetes to come together, meet others their age and
> develop new, innovative and positive ways of providing peer support.
>If you're interested in finding out more about the project contact Allan
